    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你的旅程始于古老神秘废墟上空的阴森之地。怀揣着对荣耀、权力与无尽财富的永不满足的渴求，你将在追逐可悲野心的过程中直面挑战，揭开黑暗秘辛。</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在线多人模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与最多四位好友组队，或独自勇闯黑暗。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >险恶地牢</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入遗忘地牢，这里充斥着噩梦般的生物、致命陷阱、摇摇欲坠的结构、暗藏的深渊与剧毒气体。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126410/extras/79f51cd1b277171c703399e3bebe302d.poster.avif?t=1772389346\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126410/extras/79f51cd1b277171c703399e3bebe302d.webm?t=1772389346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >永久死亡</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死亡意味着永久失去角色及其所有装备。若想带着辛苦获得的战利品生还——务必谨慎行事。基地营地中的物品均可安全存放。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126410/extras/50beb2d0b2d067fa847b6486e76c1396.poster.avif?t=1772389346\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126410/extras/50beb2d0b2d067fa847b6486e76c1396.webm?t=1772389346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装备定制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从独立部件组装武器：剑、锤、斧、长柄武器、标枪、弓或弩——选择权在你手中。通过材料、色调和涂装定制所有装备，完美契合你的游戏风格与时尚品味。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126410/extras/7b885a5a0fa310bb3d7b07015a774b7b.poster.avif?t=1772389346\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126410/extras/7b885a5a0fa310bb3d7b07015a774b7b.webm?t=1772389346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >禁忌魔法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抛弃虔诚，跨越天界与黑暗神祇交易以获取禁忌之力，但切记——万物皆有代价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126410/extras/cb3db987c8b5be451d597b5c8a328197.poster.avif?t=1772389346\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126410/extras/cb3db987c8b5be451d597b5c8a328197.webm?t=1772389346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基地升级</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从深渊带回资源修复并升级你的行动基地——利用升级功能助力下次冒险，获取更多财富与远古知识。</p>",
